---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Furniture Upholstery" description="Expert furniture recovery and reupholstery in Brisbane's Bayside. Lounges, chairs, dining suites and more. 40+ years experience.">
  <div class="px-4 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Furniture</h1>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <p class="text-stone-700 mb-4">
          Wynnum Redlands Upholsterers specialises in recovering and refurbishing all types of furniture to the highest standard. With over 40 years of experience, we can transform your worn or outdated pieces into beautiful furniture you'll love again.
        </p>
        <p class="text-stone-700 mb-4">
          We work with a wide range of fabrics including traditional materials, modern designs, and hard-wearing options for high-traffic pieces. Whether it's a treasured family heirloom or everyday lounge suite, we treat every piece with care.
        </p>
        <p class="text-stone-700 mb-6">
          We can also arrange for your furniture to be polished by our polisher to complement your new upholstery.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">What We Recover</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-stone-700 mb-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Lounge suites and sofas</li>
          <li>Armchairs and recliners</li>
          <li>Dining chairs</li>
          <li>Ottomans and footstools</li>
          <li>Headboards and bed bases</li>
          <li>Antique and period furniture</li>
          <li>Office chairs</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <img src="/images/IMG_0305-Medium.jpg" alt="Recovered lounge suite" class="w-full rounded shadow" />
          <img src="/images/dsc00824.jpg" alt="Cane settee" class="w-full rounded shadow" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <img src="/images/020-Medium.jpg" alt="Antique chaise lounge" class="w-full rounded shadow" />
        <img src="/images/043-Medium.jpg" alt="Modern armchair" class="w-full rounded shadow" />

        <div class="bg-amber-50 p-4 rounded border border-amber-200">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Get a Quote</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-700 text-sm mb-3">
            Send us a photo of your furniture for a free, no-obligation quote.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-amber-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-amber-700 transition text-sm">
            Contact Us
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
